vzpkg - OpenVZ VE template management tools
============================================

	This is a collection of scripts aimed at VE template management.
	It mostly deals with creation of OS template caches. Also included
	are two handy utilities - vzyum and vzrpm.


Requirements
------------
	vzyum >= 2.4.0

	Also, different OS templates requires different vzrpm versions.


Installation
------------
	make install


Usage
-----
	See man pages, info at http://openvz.org/ and a chapter
	named "Managing templates" in OpenVZ User's Guide.


